Featured photo by @_nguan_ Weekend Hashtag Project: #whpmyeveryday Thereâ€™s beauty in the everyday. This week, the goal is to take photos and videos that capture moments from your daily life, as in this featured photo from @_nguan_. Here are a few tips to get you started: As you go about your routine, note the shapes, shadows and colors you pass by. What details stand out when you pay attention? Take portraits of the people you regularly spend time with, like your family, friends, neighbors and co-workers. A picture is worth a thousand words. Use your camera to explain a part of your daily life and culture to someone who lives on the other side of the world. PROJECT RULES: Please add the #whpmyeveryday hashtag only to photos and videos taken over this weekend and only submit your own visuals to the project.
